                  </persName>
            . I am a clock-maker. This clock is now worth between 8 l. and 9 l. I had repaired it lately.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-7-person108">
                  JOSEPH 
                  CADBY
               <interp inst="t18220417-7-person108" type="surname" value="CADBY"></interp>
